value: local in northeastern Brazil (Serra de Baturité in Ceará, Pernambuco, and Chapada Diamantina in northern Bahia)
Eastern Brazil in states of Ceara (Serra de Baturite), Pernambuco (Dois Irmaos), and Baia (Bomfim). Status not fully understood.
